00:17:34,160 --> 00:17:35,640
Kau bawa peta Lembah Diequan?

275
00:17:36,119 --> 00:17:36,800
Sudah dibawa.

276
00:17:37,920 --> 00:17:38,700
Kita lihat bersama.

277
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:41,680
Topografi Lembah Diequan
agak tersebar.

278
00:17:41,800 --> 00:17:43,260
Namun, asalkan tetap di ketinggian,…

279
