Hadir.

312
00:19:57,880 --> 00:19:59,839
Kemampuan memanahmu
sangat hebat.

313
00:20:00,079 --> 00:20:01,920
Bisa memanah sampai jauh.

314
00:20:02,239 --> 00:20:05,119
Saat bergerak, kau bisa
memanah burung di langit.

315
00:20:05,520 --> 00:20:08,719
Satu panah menembak Raja Huku Kiri,
membuatnya mati di tempat.

316
00:20:08,920 --> 00:20:10,199
Ini adalah jasa utama.

317
00:20:10,839 --> 00:20:12,839
Saya tak berani terima.

318
00:20:13,959 --> 00:20:17,760
Karena lihai memanah,
penglihatanmu pasti tajam, 'kan?

319
00:20:31,280 --> 00:20:32,680
Penolongmu sudah datang.

320
00:20:36,560 --> 00:20:37,239
Kaisar.

321
00:20:51,160 --> 00:20:52,280
Tuan Haishi.

322
00:21:06,280 --> 00:21:07,079
Adipati Qinghai.

323
00:21:07,479 --> 00:21:08,599
Kaisar memberi Anda duduk.

324
00:21:09,000 --> 00:21:11,439
Kursi sudah ditaruh di sini.

325
00:21:11,599 --> 00:21:12,160
Baik.

326
00:21:12,959 --> 00:21:14,079
Terima kasih, Kasim Mu.

327
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:15,839
Hamba tak berani.

328
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:17,719
Adipati Qinghai terlalu
memuji hamba.

329
00:21:21,160 --> 00:21:22,839
Tuan Haishi, ini…

330
00:21:23,400 --> 00:21:24,239
Tak masalah.

331
00:21:29,920 --> 00:21:30,640
Adipati Qinghai.

332
00:21:30,959 --> 00:21:34,160
Apa Anda perlu pakai
atau makan sesuatu?

333
00:21:34,560 --> 00:21:35,680
Anda beri tahu saya.

334
00:21:35,880 --> 00:21:37,520
Saya pergi siapkan.

335
00:21:37,920 --> 00:21:39,400
Kaisar punya perintah hukuman.

336
00:21:39,959 --> 00:21:41,359
Lebih baik tetap bersikap hormat.

337
00:21:41,640 --> 00:21:42,560
Guru.

338
00:21:42,719 --> 00:21:43,880
Berlutut dengan baik.

339
00:21:49,610 --> 00:21:50,290
Adipati Qinghai.

340
00:21:50,439 --> 00:21:51,119
Tuan Haishi.

341
00:21:51,439 --> 00:21:52,800
Hamba tiba-tiba teringat.

342
00:21:53,079 --> 00:21:56,119
Di depan masih ada buah-buahan
belum diletakkan dengan baik.

343
00:21:56,119 --> 00:21:57,359
Saya harus pergi lihat.

344
00:21:57,800 --> 00:21:59,760
Tuan-Tuan jangan merasa terkekang.

345
00:22:00,760 --> 00:22:02,199
Hamba pamit.

346
00:22:10,160 --> 00:22:11,680
Guru duduk di kursi.

347
00:22:11,880 --> 00:22:12,920
Aku berlutut.

348
00:22:13,239 --> 00:22:14,400
Lututku sakit.

349
00:22:14,800 --> 00:22:17,920
Tak dipukul sudah bagus.

350
00:22:18,400 --> 00:22:21,719
Tak mengendalikan matamu,
lututmu harus sakit, 'kan?

351
00:22:29,239 --> 00:22:29,880
Guru.

352
00:22:30,479 --> 00:22:33,280
Aku kira Guru bisa istirahat
di Istana Zhaoming.

353
00:22:33,479 --> 00:22:35,079
Tak mau Guru ikut.

354
00:22:35,439 --> 00:22:40,439
Namun, bisa seperti ini,
bersama Guru dengan tenang,…

355
00:22:40,680 --> 00:22:42,160
…sepertinya bagus juga.

356
00:22:45,920 --> 00:22:47,520
Intropeksi diri dengan baik-baik.

357
