00:26:42,520 --> 00:26:43,760
Baik, Adipati.

387
00:26:55,040 --> 00:26:56,079
Kau melihat pembunuh itu.

388
00:26:56,359 --> 00:26:57,239
Cepat gambarkan dia.

389
00:26:57,520 --> 00:26:58,319
Segera tangkap.

390
00:26:59,079 --> 00:26:59,959
Baik.

391
00:27:02,040 --> 00:27:02,760
Kau ikut Shao Zi.

392
00:27:03,040 --> 00:27:04,000
Kembali tambah pasukan.

393
00:27:04,239 --> 00:27:05,400
Jaga keselamatan istana.

394
00:27:05,719 --> 00:27:07,040
Guru, lukamu…

395
00:27:07,959 --> 00:27:08,920
Tenang.

396
00:27:26,400 --> 00:27:27,640
Semua fokus.

397
00:27:28,199 --> 00:27:30,239
Semua yang keluar masuk,
periksa dengan ketat!

398
00:27:30,359 --> 00:27:32,199
Jangan ada kesalahan.

399
00:27:32,479 --> 00:27:34,800
Jika ada kesalahan,
akan dihukum berat!

400
00:27:35,439 --> 00:27:36,330
Tambahkan penjagaan!

401
00:27:36,599 --> 00:27:37,760
Jangan lengah!

402
00:27:38,280 --> 00:27:40,760
Jika ada kesalahan,
akan dihukum berat!

403
